blocks.text:
The Supplier shall supply and install temporary site facilities:

Site office: {{officeType}}, quantity: {{officeQty}}
Storage container(s): {{storageQty}} × {{storageSize}}
Canteen / rest area: {{canteenType}}

All units shall be:
- Weatherproof and lockable
- Electrically connected (230V, lighting, heating)
- Furnished as specified (desks, chairs, plan table for office; tables, benches, fridge, microwave for canteen)

Rental period: {{rentalPeriod}}
Delivery and collection: included in price.

The Supplier shall confirm dimensions, condition (new/used), and any restrictions on placement.

The Supplier shall provide sanitary facilities:

Toilet units: {{toiletQty}} × {{toiletType}}
Cleaning schedule: {{cleaningSchedule}}

All units shall comply with Arbobesluit requirements for construction sites.
Waste collection and removal: included.
